(2, 'AASHI ENTERPRISES', 'jdt.manoj@gmail.com,  uninoxhouseware@gmail.com, info@uninoxhouseware.com', '9999011407 9211921407 98112441', '', '', 'www.jdt.co.in, www.uninoxhouseware.com', '', 'I-233, Sec-1, Bawana Industrial Area, New Delhi-110039', 'AASHI ENTERPRISES is a reputed manufacturer and supplier engaged in the stainless steel, kitchenware, and industrial products sector. The company focuses on quality production, innovation, and long-term customer relationships while maintaining high manufacturing standards.', '', '', '', '', '2026-02-16 11:50:37'),
(3, 'Max Fresh', 'support@maxfresh.com', '+91 72088 81056', '', '', 'https://maxfresh.com/', 'brand_logo/maxfreshlogo.webp', 'Ground Floor, 17/21, Bhonabhi Chawl, Bhuleshwar, Mumabi - 400002', 'Maxfresh, a trusted name in the kitchenware and HORECA industries, was founded under the visionary leadership of Mr. Shantibhai in 1975 as Shree Vallabh Metals. What began as a small stainless steel business has since evolved into a global force in the kitchenware industry. In 1993, the company expanded into the export market, and today, we proudly export to over 88 countries worldwide. In the year 2000, Maxfresh was launched, introducing a diverse range of innovative stainless steel products. Our key product categories include Hotpots, Bottom-cum-Flasks, Steamers, Multi Kadais, Masala Dabbas, Feeding Bottles, Cookware, Tea Jars, and premium Triply Cookware. Maxfresh\'s unwavering commitment to quality, functionality, and modern design has made us a preferred choice for households and professional kitchens alike. Maxfresh is a family-owned and operated business, currently led by five close family members who are passionate about taking the brand to new heights.', 'https://vibrantindiatrade.in/product/93', 'https://vibrantindiatrade.in/product/93', 'https://vibrantindiatrade.in/product/93', 'https://vibrantindiatrade.in/product/93', '2026-01-06 11:24:27'),
(4, 'Garuda Overseas', 'info@garudaoverseas.com', '9998111777', '', '', 'www.garudaoverseas.com', 'brand_logo/garudalogo.png', '307, GVMM, Odhav Ring Road, Ahmedabad - 382410', 'GARUDA stands for the majestic Eagle soaring high in the air, sharp & agile, always ahead and this has been the guiding spirit at GARUDA stainless steel industries. Ahead of Time has been the watchword at GARUDA and the company has always lived up to this laudable spirit and in the process has earned accolades & encomiums from all its stake holders. GARUDA was established in the year 1980 and very soon, bringing innovation in every aspect of its performance, the company endeared itself to all and built up the reputation that has been envy to others.', '', '', '', '', '2026-01-06 11:28:09'),
(5, 'Bhalaria Metal Craft', 'sale@bhalariametal.com', '9820026924', NULL, '', 'www.bhalaria.com', 'brand_logo/bhalarialogo.webp', 'K-Todi Industrial Estate, Radhswami Satsang Road, Bhayander (W),Thane -401101', 'We are glad to introduce ourselves as a manufacturer and exporter of a number of Stainless Steel products of Flatware & HollowWare for Institutions, Household, Gifts and Sales Promotion uses. We specialize in products for Restaurant supplies like Bars, Desserts, Table, Beverage, Sea Food service, Stainless Steel Bathroom accessories & Giftwares. We also manufacture Platters & Trays, Smallwares, Fabricated products, Spoons & Tongs and Original Equipment Parts.', '', '', '', '', '2026-01-06 11:30:51'),
(6, 'Shri and Sam', 'info@shriandsam.com', '8199898904', '', '', 'https://shriandsam.com/', 'brand_logo/shriandsam.png', 'Plot No. 120-121, HSIIDC, Sector - 53, Phase-V, Kundli, Industrial Area, Sonipat - 131028, Haryana.', 'Since 1984 JAGDAMBA has been a leading Manufacturer & Exporter of Stainless Steel Kitchenware, Cutlery, Kitchen Tools, Hotelware, and Petware. Since its inception, JAGDAMBA emerged as a leader in breakthrough innovation with Stainless Steel ware. It scaled new heights in manufacturing Stainless Steel metal press components and fabricated items with exports worldwide. We provide OEM services also. Believing in values of quality & commitment and continuous endeavor to satisfy customers JAGDAMBA is dedicated to serving.', '', '', '', '', '2026-01-06 11:33:01'),
